events.name: Adopting Continuous Delivery - Why, What, How? - Nathen Harvey, Google
events.description:
Teams often face a number of key blockers when adopting continuous delivery. This talk is a survey of the capabilities that teams can use to decrease delivery lead time and increase deployment frequency, while maintaining quality and security. Continuously improving these capabilities will help teams move from irregular, error-prone deployments to being able to safely deploy change on-demand.

Nathen Harvey - Google Cloud
